C shielding\nmeasurements, we construct a piecewise E(J) law that spans over 8 orders of\nmagnitude of the electric field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2010 06:14:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
